snippet.title: 【ENG】SNK VS. CAPCOM SVC CHAOS｜Trailer
snippet.description:
SNK and CAPCOM legends clash in this star-studded crossover fighting game!
The 2003 arcade hit SVC CHAOS is back and better than ever! Steam version out now! Nintendo Switch™, PlayStation®4, and GOG.com versions out July 22!
